<a name="Special_form_variables"></a>
<h1>Special form variables</h1>
<p>
Note that this list does not include any of the Interchange
<a href="http://www.interchange-rtfm.pullingshots.ca/icdocs/Search_parameters.html" title="Search parameters">search engine parameters</a>,
which also happen to be prefixed with &quot;<span class="fixedwidth">mv_</span>&quot;.
</p>
